Thanks man, does it work on 5.03 Gen-C?

i use iso tool 1.6 to patch the game and it works on my psp 1003 5.00 m33-6

google iso tool 1.6 and download it, put the iso tool folder in your memory stick [PSP/GAME folder] open the iso tool as a game, once open there are options, look for the ModNation.iso file highlight and press x, another options will come out and choose PATCH, under this select and try Kernal Library 0 first or Z, whichever will work, [it will say updated something like if the option works] exit iso tool [use Home or the triangle button] and play the game
hope it will work for you too!!
thx alot for this game man. n dude the iso tool from 1.6 to the latest pach the game for me now i am running this game on my CFW 5.00m33-6 kool!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
